cyber security tests and audits
  pennetration testing
  vulnerability assessment
  security audits
There are 4 key areas to focus on while testing and auditing they are: Asset, Threat, Vulnerabiity, and Risk
Pentest approaches
  Black Box
  Grey Box
  White Box
When planning a pennetration test you will need the following:
  Purpose
  Scope
  Requirements
  Restrictions
The penetration test phases are:
  Reconnaissance
  Scanning
  Exploitation and post exploitation
  Covering tracks
  Reporting
